    </p>

    <h2>Spread the word</h2>
    <p>
      Share a post with a teammate, link to the site from your own notes, or point people to the
      <a href="/today-i-learned/">Today I Learned</a> section when a tiny practical note would help.
    </p>

    <h2>Follow me online</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/arshad115">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/arshad115">Twitter</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/arshadmehmood115/">LinkedIn</a></li>
